上課地點
會計系館63404


授課教師




課程簡介
高級會計資訊系統


授課大綱
The objective of this course is to expose students to the areas: (1) a theoretical framework for accounting information systems, (2) accounting information technology and file management, (3) internal control structure, (4) a broad spectrum of accounting systems applications, (5) EDP auditing, and (6) empirical evidence on related areas.  In addition, this course provides students with the chance of practicing computerized accounting information systems.






